Class WadappsRegistry

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ej.components.registry.BundleActivator, ej.components.registry.BundleRegistry, ej.components.ServiceProvider, ej.components.ServiceRegistry

    public class WadappsRegistry
extends ej.components.registry.impl.AbstractRegistry
    Registry that loads activator from Wadapps applications.

    An application named [xxx] contains a bundle list that is named [xxx].services.bundles in properties folder. For each application (respecting order), this file is loaded and the activators are started. The registry contains a list of activators to starts if there is no applications.
